Step 2: Data Model Insights

The dataset follows a Relational Star/Snowflake Model.

Main Tables
Table	Purpose
Customers	Customer Information
Orders	Order Header
Order Details	Product Sales
Products	Product Details
Product Lines	Product Category
Employees	Sales Employees
Offices	Office Locations
Payments	Customer Payments
Relationships
One Customer → Many Orders
One Order → Many Order Details
One Product → Many Order Details
One Product Line → Many Products
One Office → Many Employees
One Employee → Many Customers
One Customer → Many Payments

This structure reduces redundancy and improves reporting performance.

